text-center overflow-hidden" data-v-3617635b><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(245,48,3,0.05)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none" data-v-3617635b></div><div class="max-w-4xl relative z-10" data-v-3617635b><span class="text-[#ff8f77] tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-[0.6875rem] uppercase mb-6 block" data-v-3617635b>VERSION 1.0.0 NOW LIVE</span><h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[1.1] mb-8" data-v-3617635b> Powerful Search for <br data-v-3617635b><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff8f77] to-[#e12a00]" data-v-3617635b>Modern WordPress</span> Sites </h1><p class="text-[#a1acbd] text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed" data-v-3617635b> Transform your standard WordPress search into a high-performance, deep-indexed architectural component built for scale. </p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center" data-v-3617635b><a href="https://pitt.plusmagi.com" target="_blank" class="bg-[#e12a00] text-white px-10 py-4 font-bold tracking-tighter rounded-sm hover:bg-[#ff5c3b] transition-all active:scale-95" data-v-3617635b>Live Demo</a><a href="#" class="bg-[#ff8f77] text-[#4b0700] px-10 py-4 font-bold tracking-tighter rounded-sm hover:bg-[#ffb4a4] transition-all active:scale-95" data-v-3617635b>Get Started</a></div></div></section><section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 px-4" data-v-3617635b><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#ff8f77]" data-v-3617635b>Features</h2><div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8" data-v-3617635b><table class="min-w-full border border-[#3e4958] rounded text-left" data-v-3617635b><thead class="bg-[#172739]" data-v-3617635b><tr data-v-3617635b><th class="py-2 px-4 border-b border-[#3e4958]" data-v-3617635b>Role</th><th class="py-2 px-4 border-b border-[#3e4958]" data-v-3617635b>Can See</th></tr></thead><tbody data-v-3617635b><tr data-v-3617635b><td class="py-2 px-4 border-b border-[#3e4958]" data-v-3617635b>Public</td><td class="py-2 px-4 border-b border-[#3e4958]" data-v-3617635b>Published posts only</td></tr><tr data-v-3617635b><td class="py-2 px-4 border-b border-[#3e4958]" data-v-3617635b>Author</td><td class="py-2 px-4 border-b border-[#3e4958]" data-v-3617635b>Own drafts/pending + all published</td></tr><tr data-v-3617635b><td class="py-2 px-4" data-v-3617635b>Admin/Editor</td><td class="py-2 px-4" data-v-3617635b>Everything (all statuses)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left" data-v-3617635b><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Strict Access Control</b> (see table above)</li><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Advanced Filtering &amp; Search Logic</b> (Custom Fields, Prefixes)</li><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Rich Results</b> (Thumbnails, Tabs)</li><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Admin-Like UI</b></li><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Theme Integration</b></li><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>High Performance</b> (AJAX, Lightweight)</li><li data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Developer Friendly</b> (Shortcode, Block support)</li></ul></section><section id="documentation" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 px-4" data-v-3617635b><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#ff8f77]" data-v-3617635b>Documentation</h2><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-2" data-v-3617635b>Installation</h3><ol class="list-decimal list-inside mb-6 space-y-1" data-v-3617635b><li data-v-3617635b>Download <b data-v-3617635b>plusmagi-site-search.zip</b> from the <b data-v-3617635b>build/</b> folder or generate it with <code data-v-3617635b>./build.sh</code></li><li data-v-3617635b>Upload the zip file to the Plugins page in your WordPress admin</li><li data-v-3617635b>Click Activate to enable the plugin</li></ol><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-2" data-v-3617635b>Add to Theme</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-6" data-v-3617635b><li data-v-3617635b>Add <code data-v-3617635b>[plusmagi_search]</code> to any page or post content</li><li data-v-3617635b>Or insert the shortcode directly in your theme file, for example:<br data-v-3617635b><code data-v-3617635b>&lt;?php echo do_shortcode(&#39;[plusmagi_search]&#39;); ?&gt;</code></li></ul><div class="bg-[#172739] rounded p-4 text-sm text-[#dee9fc]" data-v-3617635b><b data-v-3617635b>Tip:</b> You can customize the CSS via your theme or a Custom CSS plugin to match your site design. </div></section></main>',2)])]))}}),Ka=Mi(Wa,[["__scopeId","data-v-3617635b"]]),qa=[{path:"/",component:Ka}],ka=Ua({history:_a(),routes:qa}),Ns=Rc(Lc);Ns.use(Mc);Ns.use(ka);Ns.mount("#app");
